  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Examine the construct validity, the test-retest reliability, the concurrent validity with the
      standard dementia rating scales and the reactivity of a novel dementia rating scale &quot;QuQu
      scale: QUick QUestion scale&quot; final for the evaluation of patients with Alzheimer's Disease
      Dementia and Mild Cognitive Impairment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
